54class AudioProcessingImpl : public AudioProcessing {

56 // Methods forcing APM to run in a single-threaded manner.
57 // Acquires both the render and capture locks.

60 AudioProcessingImpl(const webrtc::Config& config,

85 void SetRuntimeSetting(RuntimeSetting setting) override;

93 int16_t* const dest) override;

97 float* const* dest) override;
98 bool GetLinearAecOutput(

100 void set_output_will_be_muted(bool muted) override;
101 void HandleCaptureOutputUsedSetting(bool capture_output_used)

103 int set_stream_delay_ms(int delay) override;
104 void set_stream_key_pressed(bool key_pressed) override;
105 void set_stream_analog_level(int level) override;
106 int recommended_stream_analog_level() const
107 RTC_LOCKS_EXCLUDED(mutex_capture_) override;

237 // Methods for modifying the formats struct that is used by both
238 // the render and capture threads. The check for whether modifications are
239 // needed is done while holding a single lock only, thereby avoiding that the
240 // capture thread blocks the render thread.
241 // Called by render: Holds the render lock when reading the format struct and
242 // acquires both locks if reinitialization is required.
243 int MaybeInitializeRender(const ProcessingConfig& processing_config)
244 RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(mutex_render_);
245 // Called by capture: Holds the capture lock when reading the format struct
246 // and acquires both locks if reinitialization is needed.
247 int MaybeInitializeCapture(const StreamConfig& input_config,
248 const StreamConfig& output_config);
249
250 // Method for updating the state keeping track of the active submodules.
251 // Returns a bool indicating whether the state has changed.
252 bool UpdateActiveSubmoduleStates()
253 RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(mutex_capture_);
254

316 // Collects configuration settings from public and private
317 // submodules to be saved as an audioproc::Config message on the

403 // State that is written to while holding both the render and capture locks
404 // but can be read without any lock being held.
405 // As this is only accessed internally of APM, and all internal methods in APM
406 // either are holding the render or capture locks, this construct is safe as
407 // it is not possible to read the variables while writing them.
408 struct ApmFormatState {
409 ApmFormatState()
410 : // Format of processing streams at input/output call sites.
411 api_format({{{kSampleRate16kHz, 1, false},
412 {kSampleRate16kHz, 1, false},
413 {kSampleRate16kHz, 1, false},
414 {kSampleRate16kHz, 1, false}}}),
415 render_processing_format(kSampleRate16kHz, 1) {}
416 ProcessingConfig api_format;
417 StreamConfig render_processing_format;
418 } formats_;
